                },
                {
                    "name": "Trail of Flame",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "The eberark Strides twice, leaving a trail of magical fire behind it as it moves. Squares the eberark moves through catch fire, creating a 5-foot-tall wall of flame that burns for 1 round. The wall of flame <a aonid=\"4\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">conceals</a> creatures and objects on the other side of it. Any creature that enters or starts its turn in the wall of flame takes 6d6 fire damage (DC 27 basic Reflex save).",
